name "win_win32"
description "Minimal Win32 window via druntime core.sys.windows (zero third-party)."
targetType "executable"
sourcePaths "."
targetPath "build"
platforms "windows"
// The minimal window needs only druntime's built-in core.sys.windows bindings.
// For full Windows SDK coverage (DirectX, COM, modern UI) use the windows-d
// package (windows.win32.*) — see ../index.md.
